	<h1 style="font-family: Serif"> <strong> About MetaMoo </strong> </h1>
	<p style="line-height: 175%"> MetaMoo is a tool that simplifies the way you read and record information.</p> 

	<p style="line-height: 175%"> MetaMoo was founded in 2014 by <strong>Vasanth Sarathy </strong> (cartoonist, lawyer and computer scientist) and <strong>Pete Spiegel </strong>(musician, educator and marketing-guru). They were tired of constantly having to search for things in their notes, documents and in websites they had bookmarked as being "useful". Word searches weren't doing the job well because they would remember the context of something, but not the exact words.</p>

	<p style="line-height: 175%"> With MetaMoo they were able to search for a thought and instantly see all their notes and highlights associated with that thought. It is just an easier way to take notes in a digital world.</p>

