<div class="container-row" style="padding-left: 5%; padding-right: 20%" >
	<h1 style="font-family: Serif"> <strong>Why the name, MetaMoo? </strong></h1>

	<p style="line-height: 175%"> <strong> "Meta" </strong> because we believe the key to organizing your thinking in the face of overwhelming information is tracking your introspective thought process, ("Metacognition"). That is the "whys", "hows", "whats" we ask ourselves as we read and write things. Capturing these metacognitive thoughts with hashtags like #what, #conclusion etc., is a very powerful way of remember why you highlighted something or wrote something down. It also makes organizing stuff a piece of cake!</p>

	<p style="line-height: 175%">The <strong>"Moo"</strong> is 'cause we love cows. Did you know that they have epiphanies, just like us humans? So, obviously we picked a cow as our mascot because we believe MetaMoo helps people gain insights and epiphanies faster. 
	</p>
